theorem interior_closure_interior_closure_eq {α : Type*} [TopologicalSpace α] (A : Set α) :
    interior (closure (interior (closure A))) = interior (closure A) := by
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  · intro x hx
    have hsubset : closure (interior (closure A)) ⊆ closure A :=
      closure_mono (interior_subset : interior (closure A) ⊆ closure A)
    exact (interior_mono hsubset) hx
  ·
    have hsubset : interior (closure A) ⊆ closure (interior (closure A)) := by
      intro x hx
      exact subset_closure hx
    have hIsOpen : IsOpen (interior (closure A)) := isOpen_interior
    exact interior_maximal hsubset hIsOpen

theorem Topology.interior_closure_interior_subset_interior_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} :
    interior (closure (interior A)) ⊆ interior (closure A) := by
  intro x hx
  have hsubset : closure (interior A) ⊆ closure A := by
    have h : interior A ⊆ A := interior_subset
    exact closure_mono h
  exact (interior_mono hsubset) hx

theorem Topology.P2_implies_P3 {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    Topology.P2 (A := A) → Topology.P3 (A := A) := by
  intro hP2
  dsimp [Topology.P2, Topology.P3] at *
  intro x hx
  have hx' : x ∈ interior (closure (interior A)) := hP2 hx
  have hsubset : closure (interior A) ⊆ closure A := by
    have h : interior A ⊆ A := interior_subset
    exact closure_mono h
  exact (interior_mono hsubset) hx'

theorem Topology.P1_implies_interior_closure_interior_eq_interior_closure {X : Type*}
    [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    Topology.P1 (A := A) →
    interior (closure (interior A)) = interior (closure A) := by
  intro hP1
  have hEq : closure A = closure (interior A) :=
    Topology.closure_eq_closure_interior_of_P1 (A := A) hP1
  have hsubset₁ : interior (closure (interior A)) ⊆ interior (closure A) :=
    Topology.interior_closure_interior_subset_interior_closure (A := A)
  have hsubset₂ : interior (closure A) ⊆ interior (closure (interior A)) := by
    have hrefl : interior (closure A) ⊆ interior (closure A) := Set.Subset.rfl
    simpa [hEq.symm] using hrefl
  exact Set.Subset.antisymm hsubset₁ hsubset₂

theorem Topology.P3_of_isOpen {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hA : IsOpen A) : Topology.P3 (A := A) := by
  dsimp [Topology.P3]
  intro x hx
  have hsubset : A ⊆ closure A := subset_closure
  have hInc : A ⊆ interior (closure A) := interior_maximal hsubset hA
  exact hInc hx
